description:
637 E 1st St UNIT 204, South Boston, MA 02127 is a condo home that contains 1,253 sq ft and was built in 2013. It contains 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This home last sold for $1,000,000 in September 2024. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $1,008,900. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $4,766/mo.
